<item>
            <title>[PIG-293] order by * goes into infinite loop</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-293</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Scripts with order by * go into an infinite loop.  Worse yet, they appear to be reporting progress to hadoop in this loop, and thus are never terminated.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12399740">PIG-293</key>
            <summary>order by * goes into infinite loop</summary>
